{
    "chapter": 96,
    "verses": {
        "1": {
            "verses": {
                "96:1": {
                    "id": 1
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！你当以‘奉你的创造万物的主的名义’开始宣读真主所启示你的，</p>"
        },
        "2": {
            "verses": {
                "96:2": {
                    "id": 2
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>祂以曾是精液，后成为一块固体的血液而创造了人类。</p>"
        },
        "3": {
            "verses": {
                "96:3": {
                    "id": 3
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！你当宣读真主降于你的启示，你的主是最慷慨的，任何慷慨者较之祂的慷慨都望尘莫及，祂是博施的、善给的。</p>"
        },
        "4": {
            "verses": {
                "96:4": {
                    "id": 4
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>是祂教授了人类用笔书写。</p>"
        },
        "5": {
            "verses": {
                "96:5": {
                    "id": 5
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>祂使人类知道自己所不知道的东西，</p>"
        },
        "6": {
            "verses": {
                "96:6": {
                    "id": 6
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>真的！就像艾卜•哲海利那样，超越和挑战真主的法度,</p>"
        },
        "7": {
            "verses": {
                "96:7": {
                    "id": 7
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>以便他看到自己的地位和财产都无益于他的那一刻；</p>"
        },
        "8": {
            "verses": {
                "96:8": {
                    "id": 8
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>众人啊！复活日，你们都将回归到真主那里，祂将对你们做以报偿。</p>"
        },
        "9": {
            "verses": {
                "96:9": {
                    "id": 9
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>你见过比艾卜•哲海利的结局更惊悚的事情吗？</p>"
        },
        "10": {
            "verses": {
                "96:10": {
                    "id": 10
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>如果穆罕默德（愿主福安之）去克尔白前礼拜，他定加以阻挠；</p>"
        },
        "11": {
            "verses": {
                "96:11": {
                    "id": 11
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>你看见，如果这个禁止者遵循养主的明证和证据呢？</p>"
        },
        "12": {
            "verses": {
                "96:12": {
                    "id": 12
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>或命令人们遵循真主命令，远离真主禁令而敬畏真主，他还会有如此结局吗？</p>"
        },
        "13": {
            "verses": {
                "96:13": {
                    "id": 13
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>你看见，如果这个对使者带来的真理禁止并加以拒绝者，难道他不畏惧真主吗？</p>"
        },
        "14": {
            "verses": {
                "96:14": {
                    "id": 14
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>难道禁止我的仆人礼拜之人，他不知道真主全知他的所作所为，是洞察万物的吗？</p>"
        },
        "15": {
            "verses": {
                "96:15": {
                    "id": 15
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>事情并不像这个愚人想象的那样，如果他还不停止对我仆人的伤害和否认，那么，我会抓住他前额的头发将他拽入火狱。</p>"
        },
        "16": {
            "verses": {
                "96:16": {
                    "id": 16
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>那前额的主人必是说话撒谎，干事出错之人。</p>"
        },
        "17": {
            "verses": {
                "96:17": {
                    "id": 17
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>当抓住前额的头发将他拽入火狱之时，让他去召唤他的同坐之人，帮助他们免除惩罚，得以解救。</p>"
        },
        "18": {
            "verses": {
                "96:18": {
                    "id": 18
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我将召集从不违反真主禁令、谨守真主命令的，看管火狱的强悍天使，让他看看这两伙人，那伙人更强，更有能力。</p>"
        },
        "19": {
            "verses": {
                "96:19": {
                    "id": 19
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>事情并不像这个不义之人想象的那样，会伤害到你，你不要服从他的命令和禁令，你应向真主叩头，你当以顺从接近他，因为顺从是可以接近他的。</p>"
        }
    }
}